  <brief_title>Validation of a Pediatric-Specific Abstinence Syndrome Assessment Tool</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of a Pediatric Abstinence Syndrome Scoring Tool Utilizing a Standardized Hospital-Based Guideline for Iatrogenic Opioid Dependence</official_title>
  <sponsors>
