  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the validity and reliability of an abstinence syndrome
      assessment tool used in pediatric patients with iatrogenic opioid dependence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
